{"Sid":0,"Did":118249,"Id":"282767","Title":"喚醒堂","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-23/d5762221-76ee-4739-b042-ac0232cc08bc/collection/3728422a-fb64-4338-b4df-bccc6c89870f/108-sea-pa-116-201911090220105dc546ef2fc1a0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n鸞堂起源於清末明初時期，其主要祭祀神明為「恩主」。喚醒堂是頭城第一座鑾堂，原為頭城當地宿儒吳祥煇書房。1895年，吳祥煇先生有感於時下各地兵火頻傳，百姓民不聊生，因此決心將自己的書房改為鸞堂，希望透過宗教來慰藉人民的徬徨無助。鑾堂除了建立信仰支柱外，同時也開辦私塾、詩社等，透過教育改善當地陋習，如吸食鴉片等。由於烏石港貿易往來頻繁，鸞堂文化得以散播至全台灣，可以說喚醒堂之於全台鸞堂文化，影響甚遠。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.821992","Keyword_Latitude":"24.85736","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/C73D270F-C3AD-4CD3-A6D9-632B0A30489A","Original_Identifier":"282767","Keyword_Subject_1":"空間、地域與遷徙","alias":"","Keywords":"吳祥煇 / 喚醒堂 / 鸞堂文化","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/23 23:50:53","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣頭城鎮纘祥路39號","longitude":"121.821992","latitude":"24.85736","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"莊文生;鐘碧娟;徐永昶","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-23/d5762221-76ee-4739-b042-ac0232cc08bc/collectionOpen/7ae6becd-af3c-486f-b8c8-1ade178116f4/108-sea-pa-116-re-201911090221405dc546ef2fc1a0.jpg"}}